description: Turf N Surf Po' Boy brings Austin a traditional southern sandwich classic on a seafood centered menu. If you're feeling frisky for lunch, try Turf n Surf's catfish and shrimp basket. It comes with a side of handcut fries and a portion of salad. Other southern-inspired menu items include Grilled Mahi Mahi Taco, Étouffée Fries, Blackened Ahi Tuna Po Boy, Blackened Blue Marlin Tacos, Blackened Catfish Po Boy's with or without veggies.
name: Turf N Surf Po' Boy
